channel.title: Register SQL Error
channel.description:
Hey everyone. I currently have a IPB that's nulled by Illusions. Been setting up the site and I realized that for some reason, users can't register with the site.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/WLsFSBJ.png[/img]
I went and added questions in, and for some reason it's still not working. Any input and help?

item.title: Register SQL Error
item.dc:creator: @D3i7y D3i7y
item.description:
@D3i7y wrote:

i would have to agree it’s 30USD a month for subscription under various plans. You can buy it at their website under the button on the top right of their webpage.

Also from my experience nulled software causes many security issues because to null it you must remove authentication source code. i can not speak for Illusions but most software even if done right, others still add hidden code to either infect the people using the site and or software. personally I’ve ran across shells hiding inside the software but i haven’t done much of anything aside from legal payments in the last few years. it solves so many problems and causes no legal issues.
